<DIV1 TYPE="title page">
<PB REF="024253_0002_0FC5DAC7FA915CC8">
<P>THE WONDERFUL LIFE, AND SURPRISING ADVENTURES Of that RENOWNED HERO <HI>ROBINSON CRUSOE,</HI> Who lived Twenty-eight Years ON AN UNINHABITED ISLAND, Which he afterwards colonised.</P>
<P>BOSTON: Printed and Sold by J. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 words"> CAMBRIDGE, near <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span"> 1792.</P>
